Combine beans, hot sauce, ranch dressing, garlic, and oil in a food processor. Pulse, adding water as necessary to improve consistency until desired consistency is reached, 8 to 10 pulses. Top with crumbled blue cheese and a drizzle of more hot sauce. Serve with Snack Factory(R) Pretzel Crisps(R) and assorted vegetables for dipping. Top with blue cheese and an optional drizzle of hot sauce. Serve with Snack Factory(R) Pretzel Crisps(R) and assorted veggie sticks like carrots and celery.